<xref type="reprint from" targOrder="U" from="ROOT" to="DITTO" n="p.oxy;1;161" evaluate="all">POxy1,161</xref></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Δημήτριος Ἡρακλείδῃ πατρὶ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>οὐκ ἀκόλουθον πρᾶγμα ἐποίησας ἐνεδρεύσας τὰς τροφὰς τῶν κτηνῶν 

    <lb n="3"/>τῆς Σεναώ, ἔκπαλαι ἐπισταλεὶς δώδεκα <num value="12"/> σαργάνας χόρτου ἐκεῖ ἀποστεῖλαι 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ μὴ πέμψας, ὡς ἐκ τούτου κινδυνεύειν τὰ κτήνη διαφθαρῆναι. τῶν 

    <lb n="5"/>οὖν κτηνῶν κακῶς ἐχόντων καὶ τῆς γῆς διὰ τοῦτο μὴ ποτιζομένης ἠπεί-

    <lb n="6"/>χθην καὶ νῦν σοι γράψαι ὅπως αὐτῆς ὥρας <subst><add place="inline">γομωθῆναι</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">γομω<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">σασ</del>θηναι</del></subst> ἐπιτηδείως τὰς σαργάνας 

    <lb n="7"/>ποιήσας ἀποστείλῃς. τῇ γὰρ ἀσχολίᾳ μου <sic>γαρ</sic> ἔδ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ξας ἐπεγ<g type="apostrophe"/>γελᾶν. 

    <lb n="8"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε πολλοῖς χρόνοις 

    <lb n="9"/>εὔχομαι. </ab></div><div n="meta.31327" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.31327" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="276" notAfter="400">spätes III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.31327" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">938</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">31327</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">6</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">938</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;6;938" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.31327" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.31327" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">P.Oxy. I 161 descr.</bibl></div><div n="meta.31327" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de" default="NO"><head lang="de">Deutsch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Schubart, Ein Jahrtausend am Nil (1912) 84 und (1923) 86.</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="en" default="NO"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Winter, Life and Letters (1933), S. 76</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.31327" type="history" subtype="locations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><placeName 